stories.title: Sami tears through New Zealand
stories.subTitle: Pakistan v New Zealand, 2nd ODI, Lahore
stories.summary: Mohammad Sami ensured an early finish with his venomous swerve and pace as Pakistan comprehensively crushed New Zealand to win the second one-dayer at Lahore by 124 runs to go 2-0 up in the five-match series
stories.byline: The Wisden Bulletin by Siddhartha Vaidyanathan
